data.description: Character and updates are found when you step inside this 1950's one-level charmer. The living room has a decorative fireplace that opens to the dining area and kitchen. The kitchen offers stainless appliances, including a gas range & dishwasher, butcher block counters, pantry and subway tile backsplash. There are 2 bedrooms, an updated bathroom and attached garage that complete the home.  The 1 car garage has a laundry area, a loft for additional storage and an access door to the fenced backyard. Enjoy the gazebo covered deck found in the backyard for relaxing or entertaining. Also found in the backyard is a fig tree, blueberries, raspberries & artichokes. The home had a new roof, furnace, new flooring, electrical and windows in 2019. Central air conditioning installed  & new PVC pipes replaced cast iron pipes in kitchen & bathroom in 2022.  New hot water heater in August of this year. Come take a look, your move-in ready home is waiting for you.  ***OPEN HOUSE - Sunday, December 3rd - Noon - 2 p.m.*** [Home Energy Score = 6. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10108411]
